        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "years = (\"2000- 2005\", \"2005- 2010\", \"2010- 2015\", \"2015- 2020\")\n",
        "apps = {\n",
        "    'Precipitaciones': (816, 735, 705, 660),\n",
        "    'Olas de calor': (38, 38, 51, 64),}\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "x = np.arange(len(years))\n",
        "width = 0.25\n",
        "multiplier = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "fig, ax = plt.subplots(layout='constrained')\n",
        "\n",
        "for attribute, measurement in apps.items():\n",
        "    offset = width * multiplier\n",
        "    rects = ax.bar(x + offset, measurement, width, label=attribute)\n",
        "    ax.bar_label(rects, padding=3)\n",
        "    multiplier += 1\n",
        "\n",
        "ax.set_ylabel('años')\n",
        "ax.set_title('Efectos del cambio climático')\n",
        "ax.set_xticks(x + width, years)\n",
        "ax.legend(loc='upper left', ncols=3)\n",
        "ax.set_ylim(0, 1000)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
